OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,6,Fwith some bright or sunny spells,
OL,7,Falthough the east may see more in the
OL,8,Fway of cloud at times. Very warm in
OL,9,Fthe sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will be dry with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud, perhaps the odd spot
OL,15,Fof rain later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FDry with with some bright or
OL,18,Fsunny spells although some cloud
OL,19,Faround at times. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
