OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry with
OL,6,Fbright spells on Friday, best of the
OL,7,Fsunshine in the east. Rain spreading
OL,8,Fsoutheast on Saturday, drier with a
OL,9,Ffew showers later. Mainly dry on
OL,10,FSunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
